title: Run to Earth
creator: Mary Elizabeth Braddon
description: LibriVox recording of Run to Earth by Mary Elizabeth Braddon. Read by Gail Mattern. A captivating Victorian “sensation” novel by the author of Lady Audley's Secret, Run to Earth has it all: scoundrels and mercenaries, love and lust, jealousy, intrigue, and suspense. (Introduction by Gail Mattern) For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audio; braddon; sensation; novel
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: This is a wonderfully twisty-turny story with loads of interesting characters and connections.  The reading itself is perfection.
